title: Ducati Monster 696 Workshop Manual
description:
My first torrent


I Hate that they dosnt include this when you buy the bike for alot of money. And you should be able to change the lampbulb by your self, well enyoy



1. Be happy that you found this and Download
2. Right click on the zip file, and select "extract all"
3. Open the new extracted file.
4. Open the svgviewer file, and run the program.
5. In the extracted file, double click on the "e" (explorer) icon to view the main page of the shop manual. A yellow security bar may appear at the top of the browser page. If so, right click on the bar and click download file. 
6. Now you can select the language, and view the shop manual.
If you want to burn a cd of the manual, make sure you include all files and folders from the extracted folder. Nero burning software works well for creating data cd's
